title: Looking Back: Rhett's Proposal Story
description:
ICYMI, this throwback to Rhett explaining how he proposed to his wife also includes Rhett driving Link crazy by wearing sunglasses the entire time, Link's strange obsession with collecting brochures, and reveal their take on aliens, plus other bizarre AMA-related confessions.
Originally aired 5/21/2018.
If you want new episodes, be sure to follow Dispatches From Myrtle Beach, Link's new podcast with his dad! Available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or wherever you get your podcasts!
﻿Don't miss the biggest Mythical live event of the year! Visit MythiConTickets.com for more info!
